        "title": "Print occurrences of elements in an array list",
        "body": "<p>I need two input array A and array B.\nThe answer will be like this - if input A is <\/p>\n\n<pre><code>{5,2,6,8} \n<\/code><\/pre>\n\n<p>and input B is <\/p>\n\n<pre><code>{6,5,5,8,5,6} \n<\/code><\/pre>\n\n<p>then the output will be: <\/p>\n\n<pre><code>2 (0 times), 5 (3 times), 6 (2 times), 8 ( 1 times)\n<\/code><\/pre>\n",
